{"tid":1236038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好用音波炮攻擊！！！","createTime":"2019-06-17T10:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T13:20:21.000Z","uid":212731,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6acfbb25096aa1eea2db4dfd47b7ef5e17d98dd","tid":1236038,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"浙江溫州一幢住宅大廈600多名居民，因不堪鄰近廣場的空地經常有一批大媽在放音樂跳舞，合資26萬人民幣，購買了一套類似警方用於反恐驅散暴徒的「音波炮」組合器材，對着廣場發出警告訊息。該批大媽不敵音波攻勢，最後敗走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bwf8ZwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwf8ZwW.jpg&h=023fdcab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wphWoYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwphWoYC.jpg&h=463c6e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該套音波炮組合器材，主要由6個大喇叭組成，放置在新國光商住廣場C幢4樓平台上，正對着僅一河相隔的松台廣場，上周六下午2時開始「發炮」，播出「請遵守中華人民共和國環境噪聲污染防治法，立即停止違法行為！」一直播放到下午5時許。<br />\n<br />\n小區業委會主任吳先生說，小區建成十多年，以前跳廣場舞的人少，沒想到近兩年來愈演愈烈，「從早上6點左右開始，到晚上10點多結束，多的時候幾百人在跳，業主們苦不堪言。」業主們曾多次去交涉，要求對方把聲音調低點，但都被趕了回來，最後才想出此方法作反擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家識做啦 千祈唔好學支那鬼國咁用音波炮攻擊人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5948f10d51140707e30623a7546636fa04728f51","tid":1236038,"uid":212731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:28:31.000Z","msg":"公安冇人性 跳舞都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd0b813acf2384db317a20137c6228a347656a6","tid":1236038,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbaf62fe4808b1140ab2e4aee52f6abf3ae007c","tid":12